title: Netgear WN311B Resource CD Version 7.1 for N300 Wireless PCI Ada
description:
This is the resource CD for the Netgear WN311B Wireless PCI Adapter. This CD is for both Windows, Mac OS, and Linux. If you can't find your CD or you just purchased the Adapter, and you can't install the card by itself, use this CD.

"Instructions:
If the CD does not start automatically, browse to the CD drive and double-click on autorun.exe. For Mac OS, double-click MacWizard; for Linux, double-click index.htm."
